  "Description": {
    "English": "The shattered remnants of an <span class=\"name name-stellar\">expired traveller</span>. It whispers, an unknowable name deep within its fibres.<br><br>The memory will manifest as an <span class=\"name name-technology\">important technology upgrade</span> to aid you on your travels. <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Absorb</span> this memory with <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一位<span class=\"name name-stellar\">逝去旅行者</span>的残骸。纤维深处仍然在低语着一个陌生的名字。<br><br>那段记忆将化为<span class=\"name name-technology\">重要技术升级</span>帮助你完成自己的旅行。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><span class=\"name name-stellar\">吸收</span>这段记忆<VAL_ON><>。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-stellar\">亡故旅行者</span>的破碎殘片。不斷發出低語，其纖維中深藏著一個不可知的名字。<br><br>記憶將會以<span class=\"name name-technology\">重要科技升級</span>的形式顯現，在旅途中協助你。按下 <VAL_ON><span class=\"name name-img\">FE_ALT1</span><> <span class=\"name name-stellar\">吸收</span>這個記憶。"
  },
